public <T> T[] toArray(T[] a) {
            if (a.length < size)
                // Make a new array of a's runtime type, but my contents:
                return (T[]) Arrays.copyOf(elementData, size, a.getClass());
            System.arraycopy(elementData, 0, a, 0, size);
            if (a.length > size)
                a[size] = null;
            return a;
        }
